  <summary date="2021-09-20T18:44:56Z" status="Introduced in House">Ranked Choice Voting Act

This bill requires each state to carry out elections for Senators and Representatives in Congress, including primary, special, and general elections, using a system of ranked choice voting. Under this system, each voter must rank the candidates for the office in order of the voter's preference.</summary>
